Strategy_resp: There are many words that begin with this letter, so I made the S sound and wrote down the word that came into my head.
I made an f sound with my mouth and wrote down the words that came to mind.
I tried to think of 'a' words by sounding them out.
I thought about occupations I was familiar with and wrote them out as they occurred to me.
I thought about sport I liked to play and sports I liked to watch. Then I considered sports from other countries.
I thought about a typical restaurant experience and what I would expect to encounter.
I thought about animals I like and animals that are related in my mind to animals I like.
I tried to imagine a typical hotel based on my experiences and thought about what I would typically see in the lobby.
I thought about my own garage and what items I have in it.
